<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV71">
<l>ūḻika ḷāyula kēḻumuṇ ṭāṉeṉ ṟilampaḻaṅkaṇ</l>
<l>ṭāḻika ḷāmpaḻa vaṇṇameṉ ṟēṟkkaḵ tēkoṇṭaṉṉai</l>
<l>nāḻiva ḷōveṉṉu ñālamuṇ ṭāṉvaṇṇañ colliṟṟeṉṉun</l>
<l>tōḻika ḷōvurai yīremmai yammaṉai cūḻkiṉṟavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We did not say “ages ago he ate all seven worlds”. Taking that from me who,</l>
<l>seeing the fruit, had said “the sea is the colour of the Kaḷā fruit”, mother says</l>
<l>“is something wrong with her?” and says “there was word about the colour of him</l>
<l>who ate the world”. Friends, tell [me]: what are mother’s plans for us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
